1
00:00:01,480 --> 00:00:03,640
[It's boring, right?]

2
00:00:04,160 --> 00:00:06,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's play "Never Have I Ever."]

3
00:00:08,119 --> 00:00:10,600
[Oh Min Seong: Us five?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

4
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:14,380
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's do it.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Okay.]

5
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,220
[Oh Min Seong: Okay.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Let's do it.]

6
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:20,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: Suddenly?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Suddenly. Who goes first?]

7
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,140
[Oh Min Seong: Let's do it this way.]

8
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:23,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Should I start?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yes.]

9
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:31,700
[Lee Hyeong Jun: If there's no one you're interested in here, fold a finger.]

10
00:00:32,619 --> 00:00:36,580
[Folds]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Among these five people?]

11
00:00:38,020 --> 00:00:39,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: What does that mean?]

12
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:40,390
I mean…

13
00:00:42,220 --> 00:00:43,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Did you fold your finger?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

14
00:00:43,620 --> 00:00:45,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You aren't interested in anyone here?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

15
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:46,660
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really?]

16
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:48,860
[Oh Min Seong: That's so upsetting.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: How upsetting.]

17
00:00:48,910 --> 00:00:49,020
-So upsetting. -Ruthless.

18
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:49,690
[Ruthless]

19
00:00:49,690 --> 00:00:50,420
Really...

20
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:53,180
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Not interested in us.]
[Oh Min Seong: I'm so upset.]

21
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:57,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: The other four didn't fold their fingers?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yes.]

22
00:00:57,820 --> 00:00:59,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really? Amazing.]

23
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,280
[As the atmosphere gets awkward,
Hyeong Jun gets a text]

24
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,410
Do you have to leave?

25
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:11,780
[Please put a gift filled with your heart into the mailbox of the person you are interested in.
Your gift will become someone's heart-fluttering moment.]

26
00:01:12,420 --> 00:01:14,020
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I got to go.]

27
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:16,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: At this time?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What a timing.]

28
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:17,940
[How nice.]

29
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:18,940
[I'm jealous.] [How nice.]

30
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:19,820
[Seriously] [I'm jealous.] [How nice.]

31
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:23,260
[Kim Han Gyeol: Take care.]

32
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:32,700
[A gift sent through the mailbox
for the one he's interested in]

33
00:01:34,380 --> 00:01:38,700
[Walking towards the mailbox]

34
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:49,300
[Who are the men falling for?]

35
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:56,060
[The men start thinking,
standing in front of the mailbox]

36
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,500
[Thinking]

37
00:02:06,940 --> 00:02:10,740
[The gifts that are going into the mailboxes
one after another]

38
00:02:11,380 --> 00:02:14,100
[Serious]

39
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:19,300
[A letter written with sincerity]

40
00:02:26,180 --> 00:02:30,660
[Racing heart from nervousness
and excitement]

41
00:02:37,020 --> 00:02:40,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who are you going to give it to?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Me?]

42
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:44,220
[Kim Sun Wook: I've already put it in.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who did you give it to?]

43
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,340
[Kim Sun Wook: Hyun Jun.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What?]

44
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:46,980
[Kim Sun Wook: Hyun Jun.]

45
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,980
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Gosh.]
[Kim Sun Wook: What about you?]

46
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:50,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Me?]

47
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:58,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Who is it?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I changed my mind on who to give it to.]

48
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:02,500
[Kim Sun Wook: You changed your mind?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes.]

49
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:06,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: About 5 minutes ago.]
[Kim Sun Wook: What? What do you mean?]

50
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:08,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I changed my mind
about 5 minutes ago.]

51
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:57,940
[The mailbox where the men's interest and excitement
are delivered one after another]

52
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:24,300
[The overlapping interests of the men]

53
00:04:25,580 --> 00:04:30,620
[Will the gift in the mailbox
let them feel each other's interest?]

54
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:36,340
[Park Jae Ha: Did you have a deep talk with Sun Wook?]
[Kim Su Min: Thanks to you.]

55
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,340
[Nodding]

56
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:43,780
[Kim Su Min: If I didn't talk to you,
I probably wouldn't have thought of it.]

57
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:52,540
[Park Jae Ha: What is his attitude
towards you now?]

58
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:56,659
[Park Jae Ha: Do you feel
any subtle vibes?]

59
00:04:56,659 --> 00:04:59,500
[Kim Su Min: We need to spend
more time together.]

60
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:01,100
[Park Jae Ha: You can feel that, right?]

61
00:05:01,100 --> 00:05:04,100
[Park Jae Ha: When you're talking to someone...]

62
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,620
[Park Jae Ha: There are many types of interests.]

63
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,820
[Park Jae Ha: You can tell if it's interest
in a relationship]

64
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:11,660
[Park Jae Ha: or a friendly one.]

65
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:19,460
[Kim Su Min: There are many kinds of people.
There are people who act like you.]

66
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:22,900
[Kim Su Min: There are people who approach slowly]

67
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,940
[Kim Su Min: with actions too.]

68
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:29,340
[Kim Su Min: It's nice to get close
with people who are of the latter.]

69
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:34,260
[Kim Su Min: Rather than being proactive,
I need to feel it first.]

70
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:37,980
[Kim Su Min: I only take action
when I feel a spark.]

71
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:44,500
[Kim Su Min: Sun Wook knows clearly what I'm conflicted about.]
[Park Jae Ha: Oh, really?]

72
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,900
[Park Jae Ha: That's good.]

73
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:51,860
[Kim Su Min: Rather than someone
who takes the initiative,]

74
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:56,500
[Kim Su Min: Sun Wook is also the type
to take action only after feeling a spark.]

75
00:05:56,500 --> 00:06:00,980
[Kim Su Min: I don't want to get too close to him
too quickly either.]

76
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,940
[Kim Su Min: It'd be great
if we can have chemistry.]

77
00:06:02,940 --> 00:06:06,190
[Kim Su Min: If we can take it slow, take it slow.]
[Park Jae Ha: Take it slow.]

78
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,490
Isn't this better?

79
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:10,180
[Kim Su Min: To each other.]

80
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:16,740
[Kim Su Min: He said if I were someone like you,]

81
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:20,260
[Kim Su Min: When I am interested
and take the initiative,]

82
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:22,900
[Kim Su Min: I thought he might have some response,]

83
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:26,900
[Kim Su Min: but he said
I was too slow to warm up.]

84
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:31,820
[Kim Su Min: Sun Wook doesn't seem like someone
who warms up easily either.]

85
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:36,820
[Kim Su Min: Talking often in this space,]

86
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:39,380
[Kim Su Min: I think we need more times where]

87
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:42,140
[Kim Su Min: we chat when we eat,]

88
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:44,820
[Kim Su Min: or talk alone
when we're in the room alone.]

89
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:49,900
[Kim Su Min: He may be curious about others]

90
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:54,220
[Kim Su Min: or go on a date with someone else.]

91
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:58,220
[Kim Su Min: I have no right to stop him.]

92
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:02,300
[Kim Su Min: It's the first time
I told Sun Wook my feelings.]

93
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:06,340
[Park Jae Ha: I don't even know what to do myself.]

94
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,380
[Kim Sun Wook: What's wrong?]

95
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:19,100
[Lee Hyeong Jun: People would be curious
about the newcomers, right?]

96
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:23,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I was going to give it to Han Gyeol.]

97
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:30,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But just 5 minutes ago,
we played the finger folding game.]

98
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:33,980
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I asked the first question.]

99
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:41,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I said if no one of the five there
are of your interest, fold a finger.]

100
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:43,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Only he folded a finger.]

101
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:47,220
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So he's not interested
in the other four.]

102
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:49,740
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Actually, I called yesterday.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Who did you call?]

103
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:51,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I called Han Gyeol.]

104
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:55,860
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But he's not interested in me.]

105
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:59,940
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So I didn't want to give it to him.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Only Han Gyeol folded his finger?]

106
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:01,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Only him.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Mm...]

107
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:07,380
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He folded his finger
cause he isn't interested in any of the four there.]

108
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,140
[Kim Sun Wook: Taichi wasn't here.]

109
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:11,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Looks like he likes Taichi.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Taichi wasn't there.]

110
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:17,140
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Taichi wasn't there.
So I'm going to give it to someone else.]

111
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:19,980
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I even changed the gift.]

112
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:24,620
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I didn't put in
what I was going to give.]

113
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:29,540
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I put in a different gift.
How bitter...]

114
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:33,679
[Dinner time. Dinner time.]
[What are we eating today?]

115
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,659
-Well... -Kimchi.

116
00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:34,919
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It looks delicious.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What kind of food is that?]

117
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,870
-Korean food. -Dried radish.

118
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:37,730
[The men start cooking dinner]

119
00:08:37,730 --> 00:08:38,900
I love Korean food.

120
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:40,760
It smells like home-cooked food.

121
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:44,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Who's going to cook today?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Rock, paper, scissors.]

122
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:46,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Not me. I made breakfast today.]

123
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:51,820
[Kim Sun Wook: I'll do it.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I made 10 servings of toast.]

124
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:54,380
[Kim Sun Wook: This is easy.]
[Taichi: I'll do it with you.]

125
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:58,180
[Kim Sun Wook: No one took the initiative,
and I was closest to the kitchen.]

126
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:02,420
[Kim Sun Wook: So I guess, I wanted to do it.]

127
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:06,140
[Kim Sun Wook: There's fire over there. Be careful.]
[Taichi: Okay.]

128
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:08,100
[Kim Sun Wook: Do you have olive oil? Ah, there is.]

129
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:10,700
[Taichi: As expected of a meal kit.]

130
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:14,500
[Taichi: I don't know how it tastes. But it looks good.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yes.]

131
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:20,420
[Kim Su Min: How was your date today?]
[Oh Min Seong: I think it was good.]

132
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:21,740
[Oh Min Seong: But it's too short.]

133
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:27,060
[Lee Hyeok Jin: I think it was not bad.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Not even good?]

134
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:32,580
[Kim Su Min: Did you talk a lot?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes.]

135
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:38,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You went to a cafe, right?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yes, a cafe.]

136
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,560
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Amusement Park... No?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Zoo.]

137
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,410
Zoo?

138
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:46,300
[Kim Su Min: What was in the zoo?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: There are many things. There were black bears too.]

139
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:47,470
[Kim Su Min: Black bear?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes.]

140
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:48,030
Well...

141
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:51,420
[Lee Hyun Jun: Asian black bear.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yes. There were lions and tigers too.]

142
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:55,940
[Kim Han Gyeol: There were also monkeys. What else?]
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Goats and guinea pigs.]

143
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,700
G-Goats. Guinea pigs.

144
00:09:57,700 --> 00:09:59,580
[Kim Han Gyeol: There were many.]
[Kim Su Min: There are lions too.]

145
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:00,330
Yes.

146
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:07,420
[Lee Hyun Jun: What did you talk about?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: We just talked around here. Then our butts hurt, so we went up to talk in Block A.]

147
00:10:07,420 --> 00:10:08,860
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Then we came back.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hmm?]

148
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:12,540
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Then we came back.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It feels like
we've just been chatting seriously.]

149
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:15,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: Our date was shorter than I thought.]
[Park Jae Ha: It was short.]

150
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:19,140
[Cho Yun Jae: We had fun at home. We talked a lot.]

151
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:22,380
[Kim Su Min: Did you talk a lot?]
[Cho Yun Jae: I think we talked a lot.]

152
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:24,100
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It was fun.]

153
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,980
[Park Jae Ha: You didn't go out?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I... Yeah.]

154
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:26,040
[Park Jae Ha: Me too.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I want to go out.]

155
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,900
I didn't go out yesterday either.

156
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:29,020
[Park Jae Ha: I want to go out too.]

157
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:33,900
[Oh Min Seong: What kind of date do you want to go on?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Me?]

158
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:39,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Actually, I really want to play bowling.]
[Kim Su Min: Bowling?]

159
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:42,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I gotta show something.]

160
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:47,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can't beat you,
but I'm quite good at it.]

161
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:52,580
[Oh Min Seong: What kind of date do you want to go on?]
[Kim Su Min: Me? When it's sunny, I want to take a walk.]

162
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:56,320
[Oh Min Seong: It seems that no one
wants to go on a date now.]

163
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,380
A walk?

164
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:58,050
[Oh Min Seong: Let's go for a walk when it's sunny.]
[Kim Su Min: I heard it's sunny this weekend.]

165
00:10:58,050 --> 00:10:59,310
What if it's not sunny?

166
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:04,760
[Kim Su Min: But when the sun comes out,
it should be warm.]

167
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,450
Not bad.

168
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:11,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But... You can see what's in the mailbox
clearly from the slit.]

169
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:16,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You can see it so clearly.]

170
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:25,820
[Can't help looking at the mailbox]

171
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:25,860
[Oh Min Seong] [Lee Hyeong Jun] [Lee Hyun Jun]
[Cho Yun Jae] [Eum Hyeok Jin]

172
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:27,980
[Lee Hyun Jun] [Cho Yun Jae] [Eum Hyeok Jin]
[Kim Han Gyeol] [Kim Sun Wook] [Lee Hyeok Jin]

173
00:11:27,980 --> 00:11:32,140
[The men are interested in the gifts
you can kind of see]

174
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:33,660
[Kim Han Gyeol] [Kim Sun Wook] [Lee Hyeok Jin]
[Kim Sumin] [Park Jae Ha] [Taichi]

175
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,850
[Eum Hyeok Jin: C-Check?]
[Oh Min Seong: Who wants to go first?]

176
00:11:35,850 --> 00:11:37,450
-Who wants to go first? -Who?

177
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:41,460
[Lee Hyeok Jin: The owner of the most obvious mailbox should go first.]
[Kim Su Min: You can see it clearly.]

178
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If you think your mailbox is full,
just stand up.]

179
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:43,920
-Just stand up. -Okay.

180
00:11:44,860 --> 00:11:47,660
[Kim Han Gyeol: I want to check it immediately.
Of course I'm curious.]

181
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:51,780
[Han Gyeol stood up first]

182
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:59,380
[Whose feelings are in Han Gyeol's mailbox?]

183
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:07,180
[Kim Han Gyeol: I got two.
But I don't know who gave it to me.]

184
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:11,820
[Kim Han Gyeol: There's one
I'm not sure is from Taichi.]

185
00:12:11,820 --> 00:12:14,540
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm not sure.]

186
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:17,780
[Taichi: It wasn't difficult to decide.
I already knew who I wanted to give it to.]

187
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:20,820
[Taichi: I gave it to Han Gyeol.
I prepared two gifts.]

188
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:24,060
[Taichi: I prepared the caramel and candy ring.]

189
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:26,540
[Taichi: I wanted to give a Japanese-style gift.]

190
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:30,540
[Taichi: Since I'm Japanese,
I'm different from the others.]

191
00:12:30,540 --> 00:12:34,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: When we were talking upstairs,
and we talked about Milan,]

192
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:36,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was inspired.]

193
00:12:36,020 --> 00:12:40,140
[Eum Hyeok Jin: As to what I can give him
that he'd know it's from me.]

194
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:44,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I drew the Milan Cathedral on the polaroid,]

195
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:48,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and wrote "ciao" below—]

196
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:51,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That means "hello" in Italian.]

197
00:12:51,380 --> 00:12:53,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I put it in the mailbox with a heated eye mask.]

198
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:58,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: His eyes are really bloodshot,
so I wanted him to get some good sleep.]

199
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,740
[Oh Min Seong: He's popular.]

200
00:13:00,990 --> 00:13:01,740
Popular?

201
00:13:02,610 --> 00:13:02,980
He's popular.

202
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:05,540
[Han Gyeol's shy smile]

203
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:09,590
[Kim Su Min: What's this?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: There's a photo.]

